item.title: CVE-2013-10001|2024-08-06T18:09:17.228Z -- htc -- one
item.description: A vulnerability was found in HTC One/Sense 4.x. It has been rated as problematic. Affected by this issue is the certification validation of the mail client. An exploit has been disclosed to the public and may be used.
